Package: python-payline
Architecture: all
Depends: python-pysimplesoap, ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Description: Process payments with Payline (Python 2)
 This package provides a Python API to process payments with Payline
 (https://www.payline.com) which is a French payment service provider.
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 2.

